                        <div class="ud-feature-content">
                            <h3 class="ud-feature-title">Chiffres modifiables</h3>
                            <p class="ud-feature-desc">Corrections, brouillons, exports, resaisies… la vérité se fragmente.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="ud-single-feature wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".15s">
                        <div class="ud-feature-icon large-emoji">📑</div>
                        <div class="ud-feature-content">
                            <h3 class="ud-feature-title">Versions contradictoires</h3>
                            <p class="ud-feature-desc">ERP vs Excel vs BI vs compta : chacun a « son » chiffre.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="ud-single-feature wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                        <div class="ud-feature-icon large-emoji">🔍</div>
                        <div class="ud-feature-content">
                            <h3 class="ud-feature-title">Preuves reconstruites</h3>
                            <p class="ud-feature-desc">Quand ça chauffe, on enquête au lieu de vérifier.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
